  "content": "<p data-pid=\"AgoCy8XO\">既然 Daniel 写了第一点，我就答一下第二点吧~</p><h2>少量材料</h2><p data-pid=\"dShs8RHZ\">直接 Ctrl + Shift + J，输入你想要把新材料插入到待办队列的位置：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee7f94001e2e3cc84e374d6a1c82df70_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1323\" data-rawheight=\"1040\" data-original-token=\"v2-c8d53afafb2c3b8343f3c972c91d7440\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a30080c18849aade105e3fd64757ec3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1323\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ee7f94001e2e3cc84e374d6a1c82df70_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1323&#39; height=&#39;1040&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1323\" data-rawheight=\"1040\" data-original-token=\"v2-c8d53afafb2c3b8343f3c972c91d7440\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a30080c18849aade105e3fd64757ec3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1323\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ee7f94001e2e3cc84e374d6a1c82df70_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee7f94001e2e3cc84e374d6a1c82df70_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"z-PcOq_k\">这里输入 47 就是队尾，1 就是队首。</p><h2>大量材料</h2><ol><li data-pid=\"6dOwU9ez\">先在知识树里右键点击你所添加的材料所属的 Branch 的根节点（如图）</li></ol><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d49b4dc6099dcf05bf1253ad5407be4a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"543\" data-rawheight=\"649\" data-original-token=\"v2-077f8a8e4268d88f4d89912a54454166\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1a17bce15d9ef4d5999cd4407bfb7e2f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"543\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d49b4dc6099dcf05bf1253ad5407be4a_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;543&#39; height=&#39;649&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"543\" data-rawheight=\"649\" data-original-token=\"v2-077f8a8e4268d88f4d89912a54454166\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1a17bce15d9ef4d5999cd4407bfb7e2f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"543\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d49b4dc6099dcf05bf1253ad5407be4a_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d49b4dc6099dcf05bf1253ad5407be4a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"8tMEbL-0\">2. 点击 Process branch，找到 Learning - Add all to outstanding 并点击：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4cf6bc6e7886cae1c62fd72c3b9fa59_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"848\" data-rawheight=\"556\" data-original-token=\"v2-89a602c5341c34638d7121571df3f734\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-838ba341148d8ed166e7ebaf356e2575_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"848\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b4cf6bc6e7886cae1c62fd72c3b9fa59_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;848&#39; height=&#39;556&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"848\" data-rawheight=\"556\" data-original-token=\"v2-89a602c5341c34638d7121571df3f734\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-838ba341148d8ed166e7ebaf356e2575_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"848\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b4cf6bc6e7886cae1c62fd72c3b9fa59_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4cf6bc6e7886cae1c62fd72c3b9fa59_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"9zbdW2u8\">3. 输入一个数字 n，代表在原有的队列基础上，每隔 n 个卡片插入一个 branch 中的卡片。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-af272676a6011aca6d42511811119140_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"909\" data-rawheight=\"406\" data-original-token=\"v2-a6928a66dc616efad94898248f5ee815\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ff320f61f904f5778622c0135daa6383_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"909\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-af272676a6011aca6d42511811119140_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;909&#39; height=&#39;406&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"909\" data-rawheight=\"406\" data-original-token=\"v2-a6928a66dc616efad94898248f5ee815\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ff320f61f904f5778622c0135daa6383_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"909\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-af272676a6011aca6d42511811119140_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-af272676a6011aca6d42511811119140_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"_pwtnYuC\">以上就是如何将材料立即加入当天待办队列的方法，更多有关筛选组学习的技巧，请参考：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.yuque.com/supermemo/wiki/subset_learning%23ixI07\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9353ae41a63d66d6812b70a7df499065_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"400\" data-image-height=\"250\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">筛选组学习 · 语雀</a><p data-pid=\"01dwDRRi\">当然，这些方法并不常用，无需全部掌握。顺带推荐一下我的专栏：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/c_1308886122672484352\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b6546a28845e426a25b971ce7fcab919_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"200\" data-image-height=\"200\" class=\"internal\">SuperMemo—渐进学习最前沿！</a><p></p>",
